T1  - An Efficient Algorithm for the 0-1 Knapsack Problem
AU  - Nauss, Robert M.
Y1  - 1976/09/01
PY  - 1976
DA  - 1976/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.23.1.27
